{"tid":500796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵羅湖落馬洲站率試行　支那寶微信買車票","createTime":"2017-12-16T06:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T07:01:24.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6d60812841de471e2a3ae0cf919fb88eb0b830","tid":500796,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171216/photo/bkn-20171216132143487-1216_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171216132143487-1216_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=26cef9d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東鐵線羅湖站及落馬洲站有售票機接受乘客以電子銀包購票。(「MTRiders」fb)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵早前宣布在部分車站改裝售票機，讓乘客使用支那電子銀包「掃碼」付款購買單程票。今日(16日)起，港鐵羅湖站及落馬洲站已率先試行新購票方式，接受乘客以支那寶和微信掃碼購票。<br />\n<br />\n鐵路迷Facebook專頁「MTRiders」指，東鐵線羅湖站及落馬洲站有部分售票機於今日起接受乘客以電子銀包購票，支援4種支那及香港電子銀包，包括支那寶、支那寶HK、微信支付及WeChat Pay，乘客掃描該4款電子錢包的二維碼便可購買單程票。<br />\n<br />\n該專頁指，接受掃碼購票的售票機不能接受現金購票，乘客若想以現金購票，需使用其他售票機。另外，港鐵尖沙咀站及銅鑼灣站亦計劃於明年首季試行掃碼購票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171216/bkn-20171216132143487-1216_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171216%2Fbkn-20171216132143487-1216_00822_001.html&d=wZbyftWe07megWVxqYlz9QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=0c11548e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171216/bkn-20171216132143487-1216_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"57b51270a49307e29fe485f22aec5c384c00aad7","tid":500796,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"希望遲啲係全部車站都可以用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716c750ad9ee192b21f9142fc66961ae5b997b29","tid":500796,"uid":151324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"回程買唔到 等行路番落馬洲啦"},{"pid":"a7dd8f9766ce6f75f25363f870ebbbcbb1944ee4","tid":500796,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0